1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,859
In this level we will evaluate your cognitive flexibility.

2
00:00:03,859 --> 00:00:07,120
Your goal will be to reach the center of the maze.

3
00:00:07,120 --> 00:00:11,359
You will do it using your tokens and these terminal symbols.

4
00:00:11,359 --> 00:00:14,439
On screen, a maze full of symbols will appear.

5
00:00:14,439 --> 00:00:18,679
To solve it, you must start at the entrance that matches your token number,

6
00:00:18,679 --> 00:00:23,600
and pass it through terminals showing the symbols you find along the path.

7
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:25,519
But that is not all.

8
00:00:25,519 --> 00:00:30,239
At some point, an alarm will sound and the maze will turn red. When that

9
00:00:30,239 --> 00:00:33,880
happens, you must pass the token through the terminal with the opposite symbol to the one

10
00:00:33,880 --> 00:00:38,920
shown in the maze. Stay alert, because at any moment the maze can return

11
00:00:38,920 --> 00:00:44,960
to its original form. Be careful: one single mistake and you will have to start your route

12
00:00:44,960 --> 00:00:45,399
again.
